table_caption: Various clinical features of Alzheimer's patients with and without Type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).
table_foot: Note: Normally distributed continuous variables were presented as mean (SD), nonnormally distributed continuous variables were presented as median (Q1–Q3), Categorical variables were presented as counts (percentages).Abbreviations: AD, Alzheimer's disease; eGFR, estimated glomerular filtration rate; NLR, neutrophil–lymphocyte ratio; PLR, platelet–lymphocyte ratio.
